NOTES: 
More Songs About Dope, Dames, And Debauchery album by Flower Leperds was released Jan 01, 2007 on the Bitzcore label. Tony Adolescent's 3th Band; Compilation Personnel: Jeff Wolfe (guitar, background vocals); Chaz Ramirez (piano); Mat Young (drums). Liner Note Author: Tony Reflex. More Songs About Dope, Dames, And Debauchery CD music contains a single disc with 28 songs.
